### Get All StoreHouses (Paged)
GET {{cellPhoneS_backend_HostAddress}}/api/storehouses?pageIndex=1&pageSize=5&status=active
Accept: application/json

### Get StoreHouse by ID
GET {{cellPhoneS_backend_HostAddress}}/api/storehouses/1
Accept: application/json

### Create StoreHouse (Admin)
POST {{cellPhoneS_backend_HostAddress}}/api/admin/storehouses
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "street": "123 Tech Street",
  "district": "Silicon Valley",
  "city": "San Francisco",
  "status": "active"
}

### Update StoreHouse (Admin)
PUT {{cellPhoneS_backend_HostAddress}}/api/admin/storehouses/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "id": 1,
  "street": "456 New Tech St",
  "status": "active"
}

### Delete StoreHouse (Admin)
DELETE {{cellPhoneS_backend_HostAddress}}/api/admin/storehouses/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
